12 An Act relating to schools; amending 70 O.S. 2021,
Section 3-151.1, which relates to high school
13 graduation rates; modifying calculation of the four-
year and extended-year adjusted cohort graduation
14 rates; prohibiting certain student transfers from
being included in adjusted cohort rate; updating
15 statutory references; updating statutory language;
amending 70 O.S. 2021, Section 1210.545, which
16 relates to annual school reports for the Oklahoma
School Testing Program; prohibiting chronic
17 absenteeism from being included in certain statewide
measures; directing the grade of school sites to
18 include teacher retention rate; expanding items to be
included as postsecondary opportunities; allowing
19 school sites to be eligible for bonus points based on
in-person classroom instruction and improvement in
20 chronic absenteeism rate; directing the State Board
of Education to amend and submit ESSA state plan by a
21 specific date; updating statutory language; providing
an effective date; and declaring an emergency.
